<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Github on 习七</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/tags/github/</link><description>Recent content in Github on 习七</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</managingEditor><webMaster>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Oct 2018 08:26:32 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://it-boyer.github.io/tags/github/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Zsh插件之github使用</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/old/git/Zsh%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E4%B9%8Bgithub%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Oct 2018 08:26:32 +0000</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/old/git/Zsh%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E4%B9%8Bgithub%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>&lt;h2&gt;github插件&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This plugin supports working with GitHub from the command line. It provides a few things:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sets up the &lt;code&gt;hub&lt;/code&gt; wrapper and completions for the &lt;code&gt;git&lt;/code&gt; command if you have &lt;code&gt;hub&lt;/code&gt; installed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Completion for the &lt;code&gt;github&lt;/code&gt; Ruby gem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Convenience functions for working with repos and URLs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Functions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;empty_gh&lt;/code&gt; - Creates a new empty repo (with a &lt;code&gt;README.md&lt;/code&gt;) and pushes it to GitHub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;new_gh&lt;/code&gt; - Initializes an existing directory as a repo and pushes it to GitHub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;exist_gh&lt;/code&gt; - Takes an existing repo and pushes it to GitHub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;git.io&lt;/code&gt; - Shortens a URL using &lt;a href="https://git.io"&gt;git.io&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>使用curl命令管理远程github库</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/old/git/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8curl%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8Bgithub%E5%BA%93/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 Jun 2018 11:14:00 +0000</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/old/git/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8curl%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8Bgithub%E5%BA%93/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;使用&lt;code&gt;curl&lt;/code&gt;命令管理远程github库&lt;/p&gt;
